posts.post_title: FS: Complete Set of (10) 1888 R&S Artistic Die Cuts
posts.post_content:
For sale is a complete set of 1888 Rafael Tuck & Sons die cuts.  They are:  Boston, Chicago, Detroit, Indianapolis, New York, Philadelphia and Pittsburgh from the National League, and Baltimore, Brooklyn and St. Louis from the American Association.

SOLD!!!  I am asking $750 for the set, shipping included, through PayPal.   SOLD!!!
